features: Multipurpose: Our metal baking pan organizer is great for cutting boards, cookie sheets, a pizza dish, cake platter, or muffin tins. With vertical dividers, the configurations of our baking baking pan organizer rack for cabinet storage are endless!

Stylish: The simplistic design of our cookware and cutting board holder blends in with any décor. Perfect for a restaurant kitchen, dorm room, hotel, and more. It is also rust resistant, so it can function as a countertop dishes drying rack.

Durable: Made of premium quality powder coated steel, our dish organizer supports the weight of your pan or pot lid without tipping over. We have also included attachable anti slip grips to help ensure it remains in place.

Space Saving: Our cutting board organizer is conveniently constructed to stand upright or on its side to fit easily into your cupboard or cabinets. The cookie sheet organizer is designed with a flat bottom to prevent scuffs to your furniture.
Great Value Pack: Comes with 2 steel wire pot racks. Our cutting board rack measures 7.25”D x 9.25”W x 11”H with 1.25”W between each divider. No assembly or tools are required!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 28, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 3.0 out of 5 stars Sturdy, but ultimately did not use
reviews.reviewText: The racks are sturdy but I found them frustrating for my purposes. The slots are wide enough for single sheet pans, cookie sheets and cutting boards, but when removing a sheet pan, for instance, the pan next to it gets in the way. There just isn’t enough room for my hand to reach for a pan without bumping into the pan next to it. Also, it didn’t feel secure as a freestanding rack. The whole thing tends to move when pulling out a pan. Since I am using wire shelving for storing my pans, I didn’t have a good way to secure the rack.So I decided to try an expandable rack that allows adjustment of the slots. I already had https://www.amazon.com/dp/B07TQF57WS?psc=1&ref=ppx_yo2ov_dt_b_product_details for storing fry and saute pans and knew it was sturdy and versatile, so I ordered another one for my sheet pans, cutting boards, cooling racks, pizza pans, etc. It turned out to be perfect for my needs and easily holds everything. I still think this product is fine and works ok, especially if all you need are narrow slots, but the heavy duty expandable rack is so much better that, if you have the space for it, I would recommend it over this product.
